ng%20him%20as%20%26quot%3Bvery%20much%20a%20prosecutor.%26quot%3B%20Since%20Trump%20and%20the%20others%20were%20indicted%2C%20Wade%20has%20been%20a%20near-constant%20presence%20in%20the%20courtroom%20during%20hearings.%20But%20it's%20generally%20other%20prosecutors%20who%20argue%20motions%2C%20cross-examine%20witnesses%20or%20write%20briefs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump%20team%20%E2%80%94%20including%20outside%20Georgia%20%E2%80%94%20is%20following%20the%20fracas.%20Defense%20lawyers%20in%20the%20federal%20classified%20documents%20case%20have%20demanded%20any%20records%20related%20to%202022%20meetings%20between%20Wade%20and%20White%20House%20staff.%20Records%20show%20Wade%20billed%20for%20what%20he%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Btravel%20to%20Athens%3B%20conf%20with%20White%20House%20Counsel%26quot%3B%20in%20May%202022.%20There's%20another%20charge%20for%20%26quot%3BInterview%20with%20DC%2FWhite%20House.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20review%20of%20visitor%20logs%20at%20the%20White%20House%20did%20not%20turn%20up%20any%20meeting%20with%20Wade.%20There%20was%20a%20conference%20call%20in%20May%202022%20between%20Willis'%20team%20and%20the%20White%20House%20counsel's%20office%20to%20ask%20whether%20investigators%20could%20interview%20former%20White%20House%20officials%2C%20or%20whether%20they%20would%20be%20bound%20by%20federal%20rules%20that%20prohibit%20unauthorized%20disclosures%20of%20official%20information%2C%20according%20to%20a%20person%20familiar%20with%20the%20call%20who%20spoke%20to%20the%20AP%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity%20because%20they%20weren't%20authorized%20to%20speak%20publicly%20about%20it.%20But%20it%20wasn't%20immediately%20clear%20whether%20Wade%20was%20on%20that%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20surprising%20that%20Trump%20has%20seized%20on%20the%20Willis%20and%20Wade%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20took%20a%20similar%20tack%20during%20the%20FBI's%20investigation%20into%20Russian%20election%20interference%20amid%20revelations%20th