gators%20that%20she%20never%20consented%20to%20be%20video%20recorded%20and%20was%20unaware%20it%20had%20occurred.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolice%20said%20they%20asked%20the%20Sarasota%20County%20State%20Attorney's%20Office%20on%20Friday%20to%20file%20video%20voyeurism%20charges%20against%20Ziegler%2C%20but%20that%20has%20not%20yet%20happened.%20Prosecutors%20did%20not%20immediately%20return%20a%20phone%20call%20seeking%20comment.%20Under%20Florida%20law%2C%20video%20voyeurism%20is%20a%20third-degree%20felony%20that%20is%20punishable%20by%20up%20to%20five%20years%20in%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDerek%20Byrd%2C%20Ziegler's%20attorney%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20%26quot%3Bsince%20day%20one%2C%20we%20have%20been%20confident%20Mr.%20Ziegler%20would%20be%20exonerated%20from%20these%20baseless%20allegations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20has%20been%20completely%20honest%2C%20forthright%2C%20and%20has%20been%20fully%20cooperative%20with%20law%20enforcement%20at%20every%20stage%20of%20this%20investigation%2C%26quot%3B%20Byrd%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20we%20are%20disappointed%20that%20the%20Sarasota%20Police%20Department%20'punted'%20the%20decision%20on%20the%20remaining%20portion%20of%20the%20case%20to%20the%20State%20Attorney's%20office%2C%20we%20strongly%20believe%20that%20the%20State%20Attorney%20will%20not%20prosecute%20Mr.%20Ziegler%20for%20any%20crime.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZiegler%2C%2040%2C%20previously%20admitted%20having%20sex%20with%20the%20woman%20but%20insisted%20it%20was%20consensual%20and%20blamed%20political%20opponents%20for%20sensationalizing%20the%20matter.%20Court%20records%20show%20that%20his%20wife%2C%20Bridget%20Ziegler%2C%20told%20detectives%20the%20three%20had%20engaged%20in%20sex%20once%20more%20than%20a%20year%20ago.%20Police%20said%20Bridget%20Ziegler%20backed%20out%20of%20the%20planned%20encounter%20but%20her%20husband%20went%20to%20the%20accuser's%20apartment%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBridget%20Ziegler%20is%20a%20prominent%20conservative%20who%20co-founded%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fmoms-for-liberty-2024-election-republican-candidates-f46500e0e17761a7e6a3c02b61a3d229%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMoms%20for%20Liberty%3C%2Fa%3E%20organization%20and%20is%20also%20an%20elected%20member%20of%20the%20Sarasota%20County%20school%20board.%20She%20was%20also%20appointed%20by%20Gov.%20Ron%20DeSantis%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fdisney-desantis-lawsuit-reedy-creek-f7648be9327545e10d4d531f42f0bc76%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eboard%20that%20now%20oversees%20Walt%20Disney%20World's%20land%20development.%3C%2Fa%3E%20DeSantis%20pushed%20through%20legislation%20last%20year%20disbanding%20a%20Disney-controlled%20board%20after%20the%20company%20opposed%20his%20bill%20that%20limits%20sex%20education%20in%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Republican%20Party%20of%20Florida%20ousted%20Ziegler%20earlier%20this%20month%20as%20police%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fflorida-republicans-rpof-christian-ziegler-848e1093ac8d4137f1b92e5b4fbcfb13%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvestigated%20the%20rape%20accusation%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20him.%20The%20party%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fchristian-ziegler-rape-accusation-florida-republican-party-8d1cb7c6f2f3e009a88e47a735eacc4c%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esuspended%20Ziegler%20last%20month%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20demanded%20his%20resignation%2C%20saying%20he%20couldn't%20effectively%20lead%20during%20a%20critical%20election%20year%20with%20the%20allegations%20swirling%20around%20him.%20DeSantis%2C%20U.S.%20Sens.%20Marco%20Rubio%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Fhub%2Frick-scott%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERick%20Scott%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20other%20Republican%20leaders%20had%20also%20called%20on%20Ziegler%20to%20step%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20immediately%20clear%20what%20the%20conclusion%20of%20the%20rape%20investigation%20would%20mean%20for%20Ziegler's%20future%20with%20the%20state%20Republican%20Party.%20Evan%20Power%2C%20who%20had%20been%20vice%20chair%20of%20the%20state%20GOP%2C%20has%20already%20been%20chosen%20to%20replace%20Ziegler.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Sarasota%20Police%20Detective%20Angela%20Cox%20said%20in%20search%20warrant%20affidavits%20that%20investigators%20were%20seeking%20emails%2C%20photos%2C%20videos%2C%20contacts%20and%20other%20information%20from%20Ziegler's%20cellphone%20and%20Google%20account%20as%20part%20of%20their%20investigation%20into%20the%20woman's%20accusation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20told%20detectives%20that%20she%20and%20Ziegler%20have%20known%20each%20other%20for%20more%20than%2020%20years.%20She%20said%20that%20on%20Oct.%202%2C%20she%20agreed%20to%20have%20sex%20with%20Ziegler%20and%20his%20wife%20but%20backed%20out%20after%20being%20told%20that%20Ziegler's%20wife%20%26quot%3Bcouldn't%20make%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20said%20that%20a%20while%20later%2C%20she%20left%20her%20apartment%20to%20walk%20her%20dog%20and%20found%20Ziegler%20standing%20in%20the%20hallway.%20She%20says%20he%20pushed%20her%20inside%20and%20raped%20her%2C%20according%20to%20the%20affidavits.%20Investigators%20say%20the%20apartment%20complex's%20security%20video%20shows%20Ziegler%20entering%20the%20building%20and%20leaving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20woman's%20sister%20told%20Cox%20that%20the%20woman%20called%20her%20and%20told%20her%20she%20was%20raped.%20The%20woman%20reported%20the%20rape%20two%20days%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20late%20October%2C%20after%20Ziegler%20tried%20to%20contact%20the%20woman%2C%20police%20had%20her%20exchange%20monitored%20phone%20and%20text%20message%20conversations%20with%20him.%20According%20to%20the%20affidavits%2C%20he%20insisted%20they%20are%20friends%20and%20at%20one%20point%20suggested%20that%20they%20meet%20in%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHell%20no%2C%20not%20after%20what%20you%20did%20to%20me.%20Do%20you%20understand%20I%20am%20terrified%20of%20you%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20replied%20that%20he%20had%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20phone%20call%2C%20the%20woman%20told%20Ziegler%20that%20he%20had%20sexually%20assaulted%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20are%20big%20words%2C%20please%20don't%2C%20no%20I%20didn't%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20replied.%20%26quot%3BYou%20invited%20me%20in.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20offered%20her%20%26quot%3Bfinancial%20help%26quot%3B%20before%20becoming%20suspicious%20that%20their%20calls%20were%20being%20recorded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20Nov.%202%20interview%20with%20detectives%20with%20his%20attorney%20present%2C%20Ziegler%20said%20the%20sex%20was%20consensual%20and%20that%20he%20had%20recorded%20it.%20He%20said%20he%20then%20deleted%20the%20video%2C%20but%20after%20the%20accusation%20he%20recovered%20it%20and%20uploaded%20it%20to%20Google.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflorida-gop-leader-cleared-rape-but-could-face-voyeurism-charge-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705705069000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65aafdad43bb77284b9eeb8c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflorida-gop-leader-cleared-rape-but-could-face-voyeurism-charge-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Police%20cleared%20Christian%20Ziegler%2C%20the%20ousted%20chair%20of%20the%20Florida%20Republican%20Party%2C%20of%20rape%20allegations%2C%20but%20have%20asked%20prosecutors%20to%20charge%20him%20with%20video%20voyeurism.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Terry%20Spencer)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflorida-gop-leader-cleared-rape-but-could-face-voyeurism-charge-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3