C%20echoed%20Coy's%20thoughts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20control%20an%20infant%2C%26quot%3B%20Lea%2C%20who%20asked%20BI%20to%20omit%20her%20last%20name%20for%20privacy%20reasons%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20they're%20in%20my%20business%20class%2C%20fine.%20If%20they're%20not%2C%20I%20mean%2C%20that's%20great%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20have%20a%20preference%20toward%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFlight%20attendants%20get%20why%20other%20passengers%20in%20business%20class%20might%20not%20love%20sitting%20next%20to%20a%20baby%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20she%20doesn't%20have%20a%20preference%2C%20Lea%20said%20she%20understands%20why%20other%20passengers%20in%20business%20class%20aren't%20always%20enthusiastic%20about%20the%20prospect%20of%20flying%20next%20to%20an%20infant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBusiness%20class%20is%20more%20so%20for%20peace%20and%20quiet.%20More%20people%20are%20getting%20things%20done%20on%20their%20laptops%20or%20just%20want%20to%20be%20excluded%20from%20everyone%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBabies%20can%20kind%20of%20interrupt%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20she%20said%20parents%20who%20fly%20business%20with%20their%20children%20are%20paying%20just%20as%20much%2C%20if%20not%20more%2C%20than%20other%20travelers%2C%20so%20they%20deserve%20to%20be%20there%20just%20as%20much%20as%20anyone%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20pay%20just%20as%20much%20as%20you%20pay%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20other%20business-class%20passengers.%20%26quot%3BMost%20of%20the%20time%2C%20business%20people%20aren't%20even%20paying%20for%20their%20tickets.%20Their%20companies%20are.%20So%20obviously%2C%20the%20parents%20with%20infants%20probably%20pay%20more%20than%20you%20paid.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20price%20of%20a%20plane%20ticket%20for%20an%20infant%20varies%20across%20airlines.%20The%20travel%20agency%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.skyscanner.net%2Fnews%2Fflying-babies%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESky%20Scanner%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20children%20under%202%20who%20can%20sit%20on%20a%20parent's%20lap%20generally%20fly%20for%20free%20on%20domestic%20flights.%20On%20international%20flights%2C%20it's%20more%20common%20for%20airlines%20to%20charge%20the%20price%20of%20a%20discounted%20adult%20fare%20for%20an%20infant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECoy%20said%20it's%20usually%20not%20children%20under%202%20who%20cause%20chaos%20in%20business%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20I%20think%20is%20more%20of%20a%20problem%20is%20if%20it's%20a%203-year-old%20or%20so%20and%20they're%20kicking%20the%20seat%20and%20coughing%20on%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20recently%20dealt%20with%20that%20experience%20as%20a%20passenger%20on%20a%20domestic%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20if%20I%20paid%20for%20business%20class%20and%20had%20that%20kind%20of%20thing%20happen%2C%20I%20probably%20would%20be%20upset%20as%20a%20passenger%2C%26quot%3B%20Coy%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Scheduling%20flights%20around%20a%20babies%20schedule%20can%20make%20traveling%20less%20stressful.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a82f456979d73718241347%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EScheduling%20flights%20around%20a%20baby's%20schedule%20can%20make%20traveling%20less%20stressful.%3Cp%3EJustin%20Paget%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELea%20agreed%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20sometimes%20finds%20it%20jarring%20as%20a%20flight%20attendant%20to%20serve%20toddlers%20and%20young%20children%20in%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20does%20always%20shock%20me%20when%20it's%20toddlers%20or%20elementary%20school%20kids%20or%20something%20like%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20like%2C%20I'm%20literally%20serving%20a%20child%20that's%20very%20much%20asking%20for%20whatever%20they%20want.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Lea's%20experience%2C%20young%20children%20in%20business%20class%20tend%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bvery%20specific%26quot%3B%20about%20their%20needs%20but%20are%20generally%20well-behaved%20and%20%26quot%3Bmature.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20their%20headphones%20on%2C%20they%20have%20their%20tablets%2C%20and%20then%20they%20won't%20really%20bother%20anyone%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20too%20often%20that%20you%20get%20a%20screaming%20kid%20or%20a%20kid%20running%20around.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20flight%20attendants%20see%20why%20some%20parents%20only%20fly%20business%20class%20with%20their%20babies%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20flight%20attendants%20said%20they%20understand%20why%20parents%20with%20infants%20who%20can%20afford%20it%20would%20opt%20to%20fly%20in%20business%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20cabins%20are%20usually%20a%20lot%20more%20comfortable%2C%26quot%3B%20Coy%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20gives%20the%20baby%20a%20more%20comfortable%20environment%2C%20where%20they'll%20probably%20have%20a%20more%20enjoyable%20flight%2C%20and%20the%20mom%20can%20relax%20a%20little%20bit%20more.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20benefit%20to%20flying%20business%20class%20with%20a%20baby%20is%20fewer%20passengers%20in%20the%20cabin%2C%20which%20means%20flight%20attendants%20can%20provide%20hands-on%20service%20to%20parents%20with%20young%20kids%2C%20Lea%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20unfortunate%20because%20that's%20very%20accurate%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20business%20class%2C%20we%20have%20a%20lot%20less%20people%20to%20cater%20to%20and%20you%20are%20paying%20for%20more%20of%20an%20experience.%20So%20that's%20what%20we%20give%20as%20opposed%20to%20main%20cabin.%20There%20are%20200%20plus%20people%2C%20so%20you%20won't%20get%20that%20personalized%20experience.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Lea%20said%20parents%20can%20make%20their%