-worth%2Fphotostory%2F106997989.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BExpected%20President's%20Rule%26quot%3B%3A%20Mizoram%20Chief%20Minister%20On%20Manipur%20Violence%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20fresh%20violence%20in%20Manipur%2C%20neighbouring%20Mizoram's%20Chief%20Minister%20Laldohuma%20has%20said%20he%20has%20been%20expecting%20President's%20rule%20to%20be%20imposed%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20(President's%20rule)%20is%20what%20we%20are%20expecting%20as%20it%20(violence)%20has%20gone%20on%20for%20very%20long.%20The%20situation%20does%20not%20change%2C%20and%20sometimes%20it%20becomes%20worse%2C%26quot%3B%20Laldohuma%20told%20reporters%20at%20the%2071st%20Plenary%20Session%20of%20the%20North%20East%20Council%20in%20Meghalaya's%20Shillong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20has%20to%20be%20a%20solution%20between%20the%20government%20of%20India%2C%20government%20of%20Manipur%20and%20tribal%20leaders%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20newly%20elected%20Mizoram%20Chief%20Minister%20said%2C%20adding%20%26quot%3Bthe%20buck%20stops%20at%20the%20Home%20Ministry%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMizoram%20has%20sheltered%20hundreds%20of%20people%20from%20the%20Kuki%20tribes%20who%20have%20come%20from%20violence-hit%20Manipur%2C%20a%20state%20ruled%20by%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Indian%20Constitution%20provides%20that%20they%20can%20settle%20anywhere%20in%20the%20country.%20Unless%20normalcy%20returns%20to%20Manipur%2C%20we%20will%20look%20after%20them.%20Yes%2C%20it%20is%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20Home%20Ministry%20to%20intervene%20if%20there%20is%20trouble%20anywhere%20in%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20Lalduhoma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20has%20to%20be%20a%20solution%20between%20the%20tribal%20leaders%20and%20the%20state%20government%3B%20it%20must%20be%20mediated%20by%20the%20Home%20Ministry.%20We%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%2C%20except%20to%20lo