0Trinamool%20and%20the%20BJP%20in%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20last%20week%20decided%20to%20abstain%20from%20an%20INDIA%20bloc%20virtual%20meeting%2C%20and%20emphasised%20the%20necessity%20for%20the%20Congress%20to%20recognise%20its%20limitations%20in%20Bengal%20and%20allow%20the%20ruling%20party%20to%20spearhead%20the%20state's%20political%20battle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20had%20previously%20allied%20with%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%202001%20assembly%20election%2C%20the%202009%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20and%20the%202011%20assembly%20polls%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20ousting%20of%20the%20CPI(M)-led%20Left%20Front%20government%20of%2034%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20election%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20won%2022%20seats%2C%20Congress%20won%20two%2C%20and%20the%20BJP%20won%2018%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705688760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Ftc8b0jl8_mamata-banerjee_625x300_22_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftrinamool-congress-discusses-new-plan-as-india-bloc-seat-sharing-talks-hit-roadblock-4895255%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trinamool%20Congress%20chief%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20told%20district%20leaders%20of%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20to%20be%20prepared%20to%20field%20candidates%20in%20all%20the%20three%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Murshidabad%20district%2C%20sources%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftrinamool-congress-discusses-new-plan-as-india-bloc-seat-sharing-talks-hit-roadblock-4895255%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftrinamool-congress-discusses-new-plan-as-india-bloc-seat-sharing-talks-hit-roadblock-4895255%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftrinamool-congress-discusses-new-plan-as-india-bloc-seat-sharing-talks-hit-roadblock-4895255%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vardhan%20on%20Bobby%20attending%20Dashmi%20screening%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705688749000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106997827%2Cimgsize-74268.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fvardhan-puri-thanks-bobby-deol-for-attending-dashmi-movie-screening-praises-his-warm-hugs%2Farticleshow%2F106997763.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106997763.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EVardhan%20Puri%20expresses%20gratitude%20to%20Bobby%20Deol%20for%20attending%20the%20'Dashmi'%20movie%20screening%2C%20revealing%20the%20film's%20postponement%20due%20to%20certification%20issues.%20Starring%20Puri%2C%20Adil%20Khan%2C%20and%20Monica%20Chaudhary%2C%20the%20movie%2C%20centered%20around%20the%20'Ramayan%2C'%20was%20initially%20set%20for%20release%20on%20January%2019.%20Puri%20praises%20Deol%20as%20a%20phenomenal%20and%20warm-hearted%20actor%2C%20thanking%20viewers%20for%20their%20support.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fvardhan-puri-thanks-bobby-deol-for-attending-dashmi-movie-screening-praises-his-warm-hugs%2Farticleshow%2F106997763.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Concerned%20Over%20Religious%20Conversions%20For%20Evading%20Law%20In%20Rape%20Cases%3A%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20has%20expressed%20concern%20about%20religious%20conversion%20done%20solely%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20marriage%20or%20evading%20law%2C%20such%20as%20by%20men%20facing%20rape%20allegations%2C%20and%20issued%20a%20slew%20of%20guidelines%20to%20be%20followed%20in%20such%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20said%20there%20should%20be%20an%20informed%20consent%20of%20the%20person%20who%20is%20willing%20to%20embrace%20another%20religion%20and%20should%20be%20fully%20cognisant%20of%20the%20multifaceted%20implications%20embedded%20in%20such%20a%20significant%20life%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20that%20by%20providing%20a%20detailed%20understanding%20of%20the%20religion%20and%20its%20associated%20ramifications%2C%20the%20individual%20must%20be%20made%20aware%20of%20the%20potential%20shifts%20in%20his%20or%20her%20legal%20standing%20post-conversion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConversion%20to%20another%20religion%20which%20is%20uninformed%20may%20not%20prepare%20a%20convert%20with%20the%20consequences%20that%20they%20will%20now%20not%20be%20able%20to%20follow%20their%20form%20of%20religion%20in%20case%20the%20religion%20they%20are%20converting%20to%2C%20does%20not%20permit%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20becomes%20more%20critical%20in%20case%20their%20reverting%20back%20to%20their%20religion%20may%20ensue%20legal%2C%20matrimonial%2C%20succession%20and%20custody%20related%20consequences.%20This%20court%20is%20only%20concerned%20with%20such%20situations.%20These%20situations%20may%20arise%20by%20conversion%20to%20any%20religion%20whatsoever%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Swarana%20Kanta%20Sharma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court's%20judgment%20came%20while%20refusing%20to%20quash%20an%20FIR%20lodged%20against%20a%20man%20for%20the%20offence%20of%20rape%20and%20criminal%20intimidation%20on%20the%20ground%20that%20he%20and%20the%20alleged%20victim%20have%20compromised%20and%20married%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20the%20facts%20and%20investigation%20revealed%20the%20%26quot%3Bstory%20of%20love%2C%20lies%2C%20law%2C%20and%20litigation%26quot%3B%20as%20it%20transpired%20that%20the%20man%20and%20the%20woman%2C%20who%20were%20already%20married%20to%20different%20partners%2C%20had%20married%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20man%2C%20a%20Muslim%2C%20as%20per%20his%20personal%20law%20could%20marry%20for%20a%20second%20time%2C%20he%20could%20not%20have%20married%20this%20woman%2C%20who%20was%20a%20Hindu%2C%20as%20her%20husband%20was%20alive%20and%20she%20was%20not%20divorced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20that%20it%20must%20not%20be%20expected%20that%20as%20a%20matter%20of%20right%2C%20the%20marriage%20between%20the%20prosecutrix%20and%20the%20accused%20is%20sufficient%20ground%20for%20quashing%20the%20FIR%20of%20every%20case%20registered%20under%20Section%20376%20(rape)%20of%20IPC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20noted%20that%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20marriage%20is%20also%20crucial%20as%20it%20was%20made%20the%20basis%20of%20plea%20for%20quashing.%20The%20marriage%20took%20place%20on%20the%20same%20date%20of%20the%20woman's%20conversion%20in%202022%2C%20ten%20days%20after%20registration%20of%20FIR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20its%20concern%20was%20critical%20as%20one%20after%20another%2C%20courts%20are%20confronted%20with%20cases%20where%20conversion%20to%20one%20religion%20or%20the%20other%20was%20being%20done%20only%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20marriage%20and%20evading%20law%20which%20has%20deeply%20troubled%20its%20judicial%20conscience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20so%2C%20since%20in%20many%20cases%2C%20quashing%20of%20FIR%20lodged%20under%20Section%20376%20of%20IPC%20is%20sought%20on%20the%20ground%20of%20conversions%20and%20marriage%20between%20the%20accused%20and%20the%20victim%2C%20which%20is%20followed%20by%20divorce%20or%20desertion%20of%20the%20victim%20after%20quashing%20of%20the%20FIR%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithout%20a%20doubt%20sexual%20violence%20against%20a%20woman%20should%20invite%20no%20tolerance.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20manipulating%20the%20system%20by%20the%20parties%20to%20a%20case%20under%20Section%20376%20of%20IPC%20would%20equally%20need%20to%20be%20dealt%20with%20a%20stern%20hand%20and%20serious%20efforts%20should%20be%20made%20to%20address%20and%20remedy%20failings%20within%20the%20criminal%20justice%20system%20and%20through%20our%20society%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20said%20that%20the%20individual%20who%20is%20facilitating%20the%20conversion%20has%20the%20utmost%20responsibility%20to%20meticulously%20verify%20the%20identity%20of%20the%20prospective%20spouse.%20It%20said%20that%20the%20verification%20process%20is%20important%20to%20ensure%20transparency%20and%20authenticity%20throughout%20the%20conversion%20and%20subsequent%20marriage%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20directed%20that%20the%20affidavits%20ascertaining%20the%20age%2C%20marital%20history%2C%20marital%20status%20and%20its%20evidence%20of%20both%20the%20parties%20must%20be%20obtained%20at%20the%20time%20of%20inter-faith%20marriage%20after%20conversion%20by%20the%20concerned%20authorities%2C%20except%20in%20cases%20of%20marriages%20performed%20under%20Special%20Marriage%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20directed%20that%20an%20affidavit%20must%20also%20be%20obtained%20to%20the%20effect%20that%20the%20conversion%20is%20being%20done%20voluntarily%20after%20understanding%20the%20implications%20and%20consequences%20related%20to%20marital%20divorce%2C%20succession%2C%20custody%2C%20and%20religious%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20that%20the%20certificate%20of%20conversion%20and%20marriage%20should%20be%20in%20additional%20vernacular%20language%20understood%20by%20the%20prospective%20convert%20in%20proof%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20or%20she%20has%20understood%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20was%20also%20critical%20of%20the%20way%20the%20magistrate%20recorded%20the%20statement%20of%20the%20woman%20by%20doing%20a%20mere%20formality%20in%20a%20typed%20initial%20performa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20asked%20the%20Director%20(Academics)%20of%20Delhi%20Judicial%20Academy%20to%20conduct%20a%20workshop%20for%20magistrates%20on%20the%20importance%20and%20procedure%20to%20be%20followed%20while%20recording%20statements%20of%20sexual%20assault%20victims%20under%20Section%20164%20of%20CrPC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20judiciary%2C%20being%20a%20crucial%20pillar%20of%20democratic%20Bharat%2C%20is%20always%20striving%20to%20deliver%20the%20best%20and%20the%20need%20for%20continuous%20judicial%20education%20is%20a%20step%20forward%20in%20this%20direction%20for%20a%20more%20dynamic%20and%20professional%20judiciary%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705688520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-06%2Fcourt-generic_650x400_71465821031.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fconcerned-over-religious-conversions-for-marriage-evading-law-in-rape-cases-says-delhi-hc-4894030%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20has%20expressed%20concern%20about%20religious%20conversion%20done%20solely%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20marriage%20or%20evading%20law%2C%20such%20as%20by%20men%20facing%20rape%20allegations%2C%20and%20issued%20a%20slew%20of%20guidelines%20to%20be%20followed%20in%20such%20matters.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fconcerned-over-religious-conversions-for-marriage-evading-law-in-rape-cases-says-delhi-hc-4894030%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fconcerned-over-religious-conversions-for-marriage-evading-law-in-rape-cases-says-delhi-hc-4894030%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fconcerned-over-religious-conversions-for-marriage-evading-law-in-rape-cases-says-delhi-h