ker%20will%20become%20CHRO%2C%20taking%20over%20from%20Bruce%20Larson%2C%20who%20is%20retiring.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20talked%20to%20BI%20about%20her%20priorities%2C%20including%20changing%20needs%20around%20feedback.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECarlyle%2C%20the%20Washington%2C%20DC-based%20alternative%20asset%20manager%20which%20manages%20some%20%24382%20billion%20in%20assets%2C%20this%20week%20announced%20that%20it%20would%20install%20a%20new%20chief%20human%20resources%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Barker%2C%20a%20partner%20who's%20been%20with%20Carlyle%20since%202016%20and%20presently%20serves%20as%20the%20firm's%20head%20of%20international%20human%20resources%2C%20will%20step%20into%20the%20role%20of%20chief%20human%20resources%2C%20taking%20over%20for%20Bruce%20Larson%2C%20formerly%20a%20senior%20human-capital%20executive%20at%20Goldman%20Sachs%20who%20joined%20Carlyle%20in%202019%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Carlyle%20regulatory%20filing.%20She%20will%20start%20on%20Monday%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20company%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELarson%2C%20who%20is%20set%20to%20step%20down%20Friday%2C%20introduced%20a%20number%20of%20workforce-related%20initiatives%20during%20his%20tenure%2C%20which%20overlapped%20with%20the%20stressful%20and%20isolating%20years%20of%20the%20coronavirus%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20in%202021%2C%20the%20alternative%20asset%20manager%20debuted%20perks%20like%20a%20%24750%20%26quot%3Bwell-being%20stipend%26quot%3B%20for%20many%20employees%2C%20and%20launched%20a%20strategy%20designed%20to%20promote%20physical%2C%20social%2C%20and%20emotional%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBarker%20is%20one%20of%20several%20senior%20female%20executives%20elevated%20to%20higher-level%20positions%20under%20CEO%20Harvey%20Schwartz's%20tenure%2C%20which%20began%20nearly%20a%20year%20ago.%20Others%20include%20L%C3%BAcia%20Soares%2C%20the%20firm's%20chief%20information%20officer%20and%20head%20of%20technology%20transformation%2C%20appointed%20in%20July%3B%20Eleena%20Melamed%2C%20global%20chief%20operating%20officer%20of%20investor%20relations%20and%20head%20of%20client%20strategy%2C%20appointed%20in%20August%3B%20and%20Meg%20Starr%2C%20formerly%20Carlyle's%20global%20head%20of%20impact%2C%20who%20became%20global%20head%20of%20corporate%20affairs%20in%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20Thursday%20memo%20announcing%20the%20switch%2C%20Schwartz%20said%20Barker%20will%20report%20to%20Christopher%20Finn%2C%20Carlyle's%20chief%20operating%20officer%2C%20and%20take%20a%20seat%20on%20the%20firm's%20leadership%20and%20operating%20committees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20Bruce's%20enduring%20legacies%20is%20the%20outstanding%20team%20he%20has%20built%20and%20nurtured%2C%26quot%3B%20Schwartz%20said%20of%20Larson.%20%26quot%3BJen%20has%20been%20instrumental%20in%20working%20to%20build%20Carlyle's%20collaborative%20culture%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20Barker%2C%20who%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20based%20in%20London.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20BI%2C%20Barker%20said%20she%20plans%20to%20explore%20how%20to%20bring%20innovation%20to%20her%20job%2C%20including%20through%20artificial%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20swift%20advent%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20will%20also%20create%20both%20opportunities%20and%20headwinds.%20%26quot%3BWe'll%20clearly%20need%20to%20put%20more%20focus%20on%20EQ%2C%20things%20that%20AI%20can't%20replicate%2C%20and%20just%20making%20sure%20that%20we%20continue%20to%20innovate%20and%20to%20think%20about%20where%20these%20disruptions%20can%20help%20propel%20the%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20is%20also%20interested%20in%20rethinking%20how%20companies%20deliver%20feedback%20to%20their%20employees%2C%20perhaps%20through%20the%20arcane%20rite%20of%20the%20performance%20review.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20workforce%20now%20who%20need%20more%20regular%20feedback%2C%20and%20that's%20not%20just