from%20Iran%2C%20denouncing%20the%20incident%20as%20an%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20act%E2%80%9D%20and%20issuing%20a%20warning%20about%20potential%20serious%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Iran%E2%80%99s%20attack%2C%20Pakistan%20conducted%20a%20retaliatory%20strike%20inside%20Sistan-Balochistan%2C%20claiming%20to%20have%20targeted%20militant%20organisations%3A%20Balochistan%20Liberation%20Army%20(BLA)%20and%20Balochistan%20Liberation%20Front%20(BLF).%20Iranian%20media%20reported%20that%20approximately%20nine%20people%2C%20including%20two%20children%2C%20four%20men%2C%20and%20three%20women%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20attack.%20However%2C%20Iran%20and%20Pakistan%20have%20denied%20the%20existence%20of%20militant%20groups%20in%20their%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPictures%20emerged%20showing%20that%20innocent%20civilians%20living%20in%20mud%20houses%20were%20killed%2C%20with%20the%20majority%20of%20victims%20being%20women%20and%20children%20on%20both%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20can%20you%20celebrate%20the%20killing%20of%20innocent%20children%2C%20who%20were%20victims%20of%20both%20countries%3F%E2%80%9D%20wonders%20Mahrang%20Baloch%2C%20who%20leads%20the%20Baloch%20women%E2%80%99s%20protest%20in%20Islamabad%2C%20during%20her%20presser.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Balochs%20live%20on%20both%20sides%20and%20indeed%2C%20their%20families%20are%20divided%20between%20Iran%20and%20Pakistan.%20When%20Iran%20and%20Pakistan%20strike%20Baloch%20areas%2C%20the%20actual%20victims%20are%20innocent%20civilians%20killed%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20targeting%20terrorists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20military%20strikes%20from%20both%20countries%20at%20each%20other%2C%20within%20a%20short%20period%2C%20Iran%20and%20Pakistan%20offered%20dialogue%20to%20resolve%20the%20issue.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Baloch%20civilians%20lost%20their%20lives%20to%20the%20strikes%2C%20and%20their%20families%20suffered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fpakistan-carries-out-airstrikes-on-targets-in-iran%5C%22%3EPakistan%20Carries%20out%20Airstrikes%20in%20Iran%3B%20Nine%20People%20Reportedly%20Killed%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMilitary%20strikes%20favour%20authoritarian%20rulers%20in%20both%20Iran%20and%20Pakistan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20member%20of%20the%20Senate%20of%20Pakistan%2C%20Afrasiab%20Khattak%20spoke%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20recent%20attack%20is%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20unfortunate%E2%80%9D.%20It%20seems%20both%20countries%20want%20to%20divert%20attention%20from%20internal%20issues%20by%20blaming%20their%20neighbouring%20countries.%20In%20Iran%2C%20during%20the%20first%20week%20of%20January%20this%20year%2C%20blasts%20occurred%20near%20Qasim%20Sulemani%E2%80%99s%20grave.%20Qasim%20Sulemani%2C%20Iran%E2%80%99s%20Quds%20Force%20chief%20General%20died%20in%20an%20airstrike%2C%20leading%20to%20unrest%20among%20the%20Iranian%20public%20who%20felt%20unsafe%20in%20their%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20portray%20strength%2C%20the%20Iranian%20government%20launched%20attacks%20on%20three%20countries.%20On%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20side%2C%20they%20also%20sought%20to%20divert%20attention%20from%20internal%20issues%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Baloch%20women%E2%80%99s%20protest.%20Indeed%2C%20Pakistan%20is%20ruled%20by%20military%20generals%2C%20much%20like%20the%20authoritarian%20rulers%20rule%20in%20Iran.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20military%20strikes%20favour%20both%20Iran%20and%20Pakistan%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Khattak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthor%20and%20activist%2C%20Abid%20Mir%20says%20the%20Pakistan%20government%20attacked%20a%20refugee%20camp%20on%20the%20border%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Baloch%20civilians.%20He%20questioned%20the%20claim%20that%20militant%20groups%20have%20safe%20havens%20inside%20Iran.%20If%20the%20Pakistani%20government%20claimed%20that%20the%20Baloch%20Liberation%20Army%20(BLA)%20and%20Baloch%20Liberation%20Front%20(BLF)%20were%20hiding%20in%20Iran%20then%20why%20did%20it%20need%20Iran%E2%80%99s%20attack%20to%20act%20against%20militant%20groups%3F%20Mir%20further%20questions%20how%20Iran%20allowed%20groups%20like%20BLA%20and%20BLF%2C%20whose%20manifesto%20advocates%20for%20a%20%E2%80%9CGreat%20Balochistan%20Independent%E2%80%9D%20encompassing%20areas%20from%20Sasitan-Balochistan%2C%20Chahabar%2C%20Koh-e-Suleman%20to%20DG%20Khan%2C%20areas%20that%20also%20extend%20into%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMir%20expressed%20doubts%20that%20the%20military%20attack%20might%20enable%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20establishment%20to%20postpone%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIran-Pakistan%20military%20strike%20may%20increase%20turbulence%20between%20Sunni%20and%20Shia%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuhammad%20Amir%20Rana%2C%20a%20political%20economy%20analyst%2C%20states%20that%20ongoing%20tension%20along%20the%20Iran-Pakistan%20borders%20has%20increased%20the%20risk%20of%20sectarian%20discord.%20Both%20Shia%20and%20Sunni%20communities%20show%20signs%20of%20violent%20sectarian%20tendencies%2C%20with%20certain%20groups%20acting%20as%20proxies%20for%20foreign%20interests.%20He%20doubts%20that%20Sunni%20groups%20may%20also%20receive%20support%20from%20Tehreek-e-Taliban%20(TTP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhattak%20said%20that%20in%20our%20region%2C%20religions%20are%20often%20politicised%2C%20with%20states%20using%20them%20as%20political%20tools.%20The%20Sunni-Shia%20relationships%20are%20affected%20by%20the%20deteriorating%20ties%20between%20Iran%20and%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBalcohs%20believe%20Iran-Pakistan%20joined%20hands%20to%20kill%20Balochs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIran%20and%20Pakistan%20are%20on%20the%20same%20page%20to%20implicate%20in%20severe%20actions%20against%20the%20Balochs%20on%20either%20side%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mahrang.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran-Pakistan%20share%20a%20long%20history%20of%20eliminating%20the%20Balochs%20because%20due%20to%20common%20interests.%20It%20cannot%20be%20neglected%20that%20the%20recent%20military%20strike%20may%20be%20a%20result%20of%20mutual%20understanding.%20When%20asked%20Khattak%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20such%20an%20understanding%2C%20Khattack%20responded%20that%20he%20did%20not%20have%20accurate%20information%2C%20but%20he%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20cannot%20be%20ruled%20out.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20mentioned%20that%20both%20countries%20had%20deliberately%20struck%20Baloch%20people%20on%20both%20sides%2C%20with%20the%20victims%20living%20in%20humble%20mud%20houses%20that%20were%20destroyed%20by%20bombs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohim%20Sarkhosh%20Baloch%2C%20head%20of%20foreign%20affairs%20for%20Balochistan%20Solidarity%20Party%2C%20said%20that%20both%20sides%20also%20have%20economic%20interests%20in%20Balochistan%2C%20with%20its%20coast%20and%20strategic%20ports%20like%20Gwadar%20and%20Chahabar%20playing%20a%20crucial%20role.%20Both%20regimes%20aim%20to%20alter%20the%20population%20demography%20in%20the%20Makran%20Coastal%20Area%20through%20migration%2C%20intending%20to%20make%20the%20Baloch%20a%20minority%2C%20thereby%20governing%2C%20and%20exploiting%20Balochistan%20without%20facing%20significant%20resistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20Baloch%20women%E2%80%99s%20protest%20includes%20a%20demand%20for%20a%20UN%20mission%20inquiry%20in%20Balochistan%2C%20the%20recent%20military%20strike%20may%20weaken%20the%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705684308000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F19223852%2FEffect-73.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fdoubts-raised-over-airstrikes-as-iran-pakistan-share-a-long-history-of-eliminating-balochs%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pictures%20emerged%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20airstrikes%20show%20that%20innocent%20civilians%20on%20both%20sides%20living%20in%20mud%