0targets%20in%20each%20other's%20territory%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rare%20military%20actions%20in%20the%20porous%20border%20region%20of%20Baluchistan%20--%20split%20between%20the%20two%20nations%20--%20had%20stoked%20regional%20tensions%20already%20enflamed%20by%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran%20carried%20out%20a%20missile%20and%20drone%20attack%20on%20what%20it%20called%20%26quot%3Bterrorist%26quot%3B%20targets%20in%20Pakistan%20on%20Tuesday%20night%2C%20with%20Pakistan%20in%20turn%20striking%20militant%20targets%20inside%20Iran%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20recalled%20its%20ambassador%20from%20Tehran%20and%20said%20Iran's%20envoy%20--%20on%20a%20visit%20home%20--%20was%20blocked%20from%20returning%20to%20Islamabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20Nations%20and%20the%20United%20States%20appealed%20for%20restraint%2C%20while%20China%20offered%20to%20mediate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20after%20speaking%20by%20phone%2C%20Pakistan's%20Foreign%20Minister%20Jalil%20Abbas%20Jilani%20and%20his%20Iranian%20counterpart%20Hossein%20Amir-Abdollahian%20agreed%20%26quot%3Bclose%20coordination%20on%20counter%20terrorism%20and%20other%20aspects%20of%20mutual%20concern%20should%20be%20strengthened%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20also%20agreed%20to%20de-escalate%20the%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20a%20summary%20of%20the%20conversation%20released%20by%20Islamabad's%20foreign%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20call%2C%20Amir-Abdollahian%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20%26quot%3Bthe%20cooperation%20of%20the%20two%20countries%20to%20neutralise%20and%20destroy%20terrorist%20camps%20in%20Pakistan%20is%20essential%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20muted%20rhetoric%20matched%20analysts'%20predictions%20that%20both%20sides%20would%20seek%20to%20defuse%20the%20confrontation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20upshot%20of%20the%20new%20situation%20is%20that%20the%20two%20countries%20are%20seemingly%20and%20symbolically%20even%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Antoine%20Levesques%2C%20of%20the%20International%20Institute%20for%20Strategic%20Studies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20Border%20closure%20fears%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%20on%20Friday%2C%20Pakistani%20Prime%20Minister%20Anwaar-ul-Haq%20Kakar%20held%20an%20emergency%20security%20meeting%20with%20military%20and%20intelligence%20chiefs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKakar%20cut%20short%20his%20visit%20to%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20in%20Davos%2C%20Switzerland%20following%20the%20strikes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20caretaker%20government%20is%20leading%20Pakistan%20into%20general%20elections%20in%20three%20weeks%20which%20have%20been%20marred%20by%20allegations%20of%20pre-poll%20rigging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETehran%20and%20Islamabad%20have%20both%20said%20they%20hit%20their%20own%20domestic%20militants%20sheltering%20on%20foreign%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20collective%20death%20toll%20of%2011%20--%20mostly%20women%20and%20children%20--%20was%20reported%20from%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20border%20that%20bisects%20an%20arid%20region%20where%20militant%20movements%20have%20simmered%20for%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20remote%20villages%20near%20the%20strike%20site%20in%20Panjgur%20district%2C%20where%20mobile%20signal%20is%20rarely%20available%2C%20farmers%20pieced%20together%20the%20events%20from%20reports%20passed%20on%20from%20visiting%20security%20officials%20who%20set%20up%20checkpoints%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHelicopters%20were%20flying%20overhead%20and%20going%20in%20the%20direction%20of%20where%20the%20Iranian%20strike%20hit%2C%20but%20we%20didn't%20know%20what%20had%20happened%2C%26quot%3B%20Maulana%20Mohammad%20Sadiq%2C%2042%2C%20the%20prayer%20leader%20of%20a%20small%20seminary%20around%20five%20kilometres%20(three%20miles)%20from%20where%20a%20missile%20hit%2C%20told%20AFP%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVillagers%20feared%20t