0Monopolies%2C%20Communalism%20and%20the%20Future%20of%20Democracy%E2%80%99%20in%20Kerala%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20was%20organised%20at%20the%20Government%20College%20Madappally%2C%20Vadakara.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESherwani%2C%20who%20is%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%20senior%20editor%2C%20said%20the%20Modi%20era%20saw%20the%20near%20demise%20of%20legacy%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20media%20houses%20have%20become%20part%20of%20the%20majoritarian%20agenda.%20Some%20of%20them%20play%20it%20safe%20by%20not%20questioning%20the%20regime%20and%20its%20policies%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20crisis%20of%20democracy%20began%20with%20a%20crisis%20of%20journalism%20in%20India.%20In%20this%20era%2C%20truth%20was%20the%20biggest%20casualty.%20The%20daily%20prime%20time%20television%20debates%20push%20majoritarian%20propaganda%20and%20create%20constant%20anxiety%20and%20insecurity%20amongst%20the%20young%20generation%20of%20Hindus.%20They%20are%20forced%20to%20live%20with%20a%20feeling%20that%20their%20culture%20and%20religion%20are%20being%20demeaned%20and%20stolen%20by%20%E2%80%98outsiders%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20ideology%20has%20not%20just%20identified%20but%20created%20an%20artificial%20political%20enemy%20in%20the%20form%20of%20Muslims%2C%20Christians%2C%20intellectuals%2C%20Leftists%2C%20English-speaking%20political%20elite%2C%20journalists%2C%20and%20activists%2C%20who%20ask%20for%20accountability%20from%20the%20government.%20The%20rage%20that%20arises%20out%20of%20this%20sense%20of%20loss%20and%20urge%20to%20reclaim%20what%20was%20once%20theirs%20justifies%20even%20the%20worst%20treatment%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98enemy%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20explains%20the%20approval%20of%20violence%20and%20discrimination%20towards%20Muslims%20and%20everyone%20else%20categorised%20as%20%E2%80%98enemies%E2%80%99%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%20has%20been%20witnessing%20systematic%20dismantling%20of%20secularism%2C%20liberalism%2C%20and%20the%20robust%20constitutional%20order.%20We%20need%20a%20strong%20opposition%20to%20counter%20such%20efforts%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNarendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20rule%20in%20India%20has%20been%20a%20story%20of%20capture%2C%20control%20and%20throttling%20of%20the%20media.%20The%20subjugation%20of%20the%20democratic%20institutions%20and%20surrender%20of%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20mainstream%20media%20has%20ensured%20there%20is%20little%20resistance%20to%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20authoritarian%20actions%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20renowned%20journalist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20aggressively%20pursues%20its%20goal%20of%20turning%20India%20into%20a%20%E2%80%98Hindu%20Nation%E2%80%99%2C%20it%20realises%20it%20is%20essential%20to%20have%20total%20control%20over%20the%20flow%20of%20information.%20They%20have%20forced%20most%20mainstream%20journalists%20to%20work%20as%20Hindutva%20foot%20soldiers%20and%20now%20want%20to%20silence%20the%20last%20remaining%20voices%20from%20the%20independent%20media%20in%20the%20digital%20space.%20The%20government%20is%20using%20full%20state%20power%20to%20muzzle%20their%20voices.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705671385000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F19185934%2Fimage-1761.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmodi-era-democracy-truth-journalism-media-arfa-khanum-sherwani%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'Many%20media%20houses%20have%20become%20part%20of%20the%20majoritarian%20agenda.%20Some%20of%20them%20play%20it%20safe%20by%20not%20questioning%20the%20regime%20and%20its%20policies%2C'%20said%20The%20Wire's%20senior%20editor.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A30%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmodi-era-democra