vestiture%20ceremony%20was%20conducted%2C%20where%20the%20western%20command%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army%20gave%20away%20medals%20in%20the%20honour%20of%20soldiers%20for%20their%20brave%20deeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20three%20Army%20personnel%20involved%20in%20the%20skirmishes%20along%20the%20LAC%20were%20awarded%20Sena%20Medals%20on%20January%2026%2C%202023%2C%20the%20others%20were%20conferred%20the%20awards%20on%20August%2015%20last%20year.%20The%20citations%2C%20however%2C%20came%20into%20the%20public%20domain%20only%20during%20the%20investiture%20ceremonies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20citations%20revealed%20crucial%20details%20about%20skirmishes%20between%20the%20Indian%20Army%20and%20Chinese%20army%2C%20which%20is%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20Liberation%20Army%20or%20PLA.%20Not%20only%20that%2C%20it%20also%20revealed%20how%20an%20Indian%20major%20crossed%20over%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Cenemy%E2%80%9D%20side%20and%20was%20able%20to%20provide%20120%20hours%20of%20live%20feed%20of%20military%20movement%20on%20the%20other%20side%2C%20from%20deep%20inside%20the%20Chinese%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20awards%20were%20held%20for%20honouring%20the%20deeds%20which%20occurred%20between%20September%202021%20and%20November%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FRy9MGJfFNrA%3Fsi%3Dh6iQyRK5OwBY17we%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20major%20revelation%20was%20that%20of%20a%20clash%20at%20Sikh%20Light%20Infantry%20Post%20on%20January%207%2C%202022.%20Here%2C%20Chinese%20troops%20attacked%20a%20post%20manned%20by%20troops%20of%20the%20Sikh%20Light%20Infantry.%20A%20soldier%20from%20the%20unit%2C%20Raman%20Singh%2C%20displayed%20extreme%20courage%20in%20hand-to-hand%20combat%2C%20repulsing%20the%20attack%2C%20injuring%20four%20PLA%20soldiers%2C%20and%20seizing%20their%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20on%20January%207%2C%202022%20was%20not%20known%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20this%2C%20on%20November%2027%2C%202022%2C%20the%20PLA%20initiated%20an%20attack%20on%20a%20post%20manned%20by%20J%26amp%3BK%20Rifles.%20Citations%20revealed%20that%2050%20PLA%20soldiers%20were%20trying%20to%20cross%20LAC%20and%20capture%20the%20Atari%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Junior%20Commissioned%20Officer%2C%20Baldev%20Singh%20successfully%20led%20his%20troops%20in%20repulsing%20the%20attack%20and%20was%20wounded%20in%20the%20process.%20The%20citations%20at%20the%20awards%20ceremony%20revealed%20that%20Baldev%20Singh%20singlehandedly%20injured%2015%20PLA%20soldiers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20awarded%20the%20Sena%20Medal%20for%20Gallantry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20these%20two%20attacks%20on%20Indian%20Army%20posts%2C%20there%20were%20some%20covert%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELieutenant%20Colonel%20Pushmeet%20Singh%20of%20the%2019%20J%26amp%3BK%20Rifles%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20thwarting%20the%20plans%20of%20the%20PLA.%20Undertaking%20a%20patrol%20along%20the%20LAC%2C%20Lt.%20Col.%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20actions%20led%20to%20a%20significant%20standoff.%20Through%20negotiations%20spanning%20two%20days%20with%20a%20local%20PLA%20commander%2C%20he%20successfully%20reinforced%20Indian%20positions%20and%20de-escalated%20the%20tense%20situation.%20The%20details%20of%20this%20operation%2C%20including%20the%20specific%20date%2C%20have%20been%20intentionally%20withheld.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20on%20September%2016%2C%202022%2C%20Lieutenant%20Colonel%20Yogesh%20Kumar%20Sati%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%2031%20Armoured%20Division%2C%20engaged%20in%20a%20high-altitude%20special%20mission%20as%20part%20of%20Operation%20Snow%20Leopard.%20His%20task%20was%20to%20navigate%20challenging%20terrain%20while%20avoiding%20detection%20by%20the%20enemy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20particularly%20intriguing%20operation%2C%20named%20%E2%80%98Operation%20Dorji%E2%80%99%2C%20unfolded%20under%20the%20command%20of%20Major%20Sourav%20Kumar%20from%20the%2015th%20Battalion%20of%20the%20Kumaon%20Regiment.%20Maj.%20Kumar%20conducted%20multiple%20covert%20missions%20deep%20within%20the%20Chinese)%20territory.%20His%20covert%20patrol%20team%20established%20a%20covert%20surveillance%20post%20aimed%20at%20securing%20the%20Siliguri%20corridor%2C%20also%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9CChicken%E2%80%99s%20neck.%E2%80%9D%20Maj.%20Kumar%20executed%20Operation%20Dorji%20remained%20in%20enemy%20territory%20and%20gathered%20crucial%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVirtual%20blackout%20of%20information%20about%20India-China%20ties%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20this%20%E2%80%9Cnew%E2%80%99%20information%20about%20at%20least%20two%20Chinese%20attacks%20on%20Indian%20soil%20was%20revealed%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20that%20the%20Army%20is%20now%20deliberating%20on%20keeping%20details%20of%20critical%20operations%20out%20of%20citation%20announcements%20of%20gallantry%20award%20winners%20in%20investiture%20ceremonies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20acts%20of%20gallantry%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20highlighted%20in%20citations%2C%20the%20newspaper%20said%20that%20specific%20details%20of%20operations%20and%20the%20dates%20these%20were%20conducted%20may%20not%20feature%20in%20investiture%20ceremony%20announcements%20until%20the%20operations%20concerned%20are%20declassified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20army%20chief%E2%80%99s%20has%20called%20the%20situation%20on%20the%20China%20border%20is%20%E2%80%9Cstable%2C%20but%20sensitive%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExternal%20affairs%20minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%20has%20maintained%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20relations%20with%20China%20remain%20abnormal%2C%20or%20certainly%20not%20normal.%20But%2C%20other%20than%20that%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20continual%20lack%20of%20information%2C%20briefings%20to%20the%20press%20or%20debates%20in%20Parliament%20on%20China.%20Ministers%20do%20not%20even%20name%20China.%20The%20prime%20minister%2C%20in%20an%20all-party%20meeting%20in%202020%2C%20said%20%E2%80%9Cno%20one%20had%20ever%20entered%20Indian%20territory%20and%20there%20was%20no%20one%20inside.%E2%80%9D%20All%20this%20again%2C%20without%20naming%20China.%20No%20details%20were%20ever%20given%20about%20the%20skirmishes%20that%20took%20place%20between%20PLA%20and%20the%20Indian%20Army.%20Jaishankar%20also%20met%20his%20Chinese%20counterpart%20in%20Goa%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20Shanghai%20Cooperation%20Organisation%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20research%20paper%20tabled%20at%20the%20annual%20Director%20Generals%20of%20Police%20Conference%20organised%20by%20the%20Intelligence%20Bureau%2C%20by%20a%20police%20officer%2C%20we%20may%20have%20lost%20access%20to%2026%20out%20of%20the%2065%20Patrolling%20Points%20that%20mark%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20in%20Ladakh.%20The%20paper%20was%20not%20discussed%20at%20the%20conference%2C%20which%20was%C2%A0%20attended%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20but%20the%20government%20made%20sure%20the%20paper%20was%20taken%20off%20the%20web.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20in%202020%2C%20that%20about%201%2C000%20square%20kilometres%20of%20area%20in%20Ladakh%20along%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fopinion%2Flead%2Fthe-stand-off-and-chinas-india-policy-dilemma%2Farticle32083539.ece%5C%22%3ELine%20of%20Actual%20Control%20(LAC)%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20now%20under%20Chinese%20control%2C%20as%20per%20intelligence%20inputs%20provided%20to%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fex-army-chief-gen-naravanes-memoirs-delayed-amazon-cancels-january-orders-not-before-may%5C%22%3EAs%20reported%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20former%20chief%20of%20Army%20Staff%2C%20General%20M.M.%20Naravane%E2%80%99s%20memoirs%20have%20been%20withheld%20for%20revealing%20how%20the%20Modi%20government%20left%20the%20Army%20to%20its%20own%20devices%20when%20hostilities%20at%20Galwan%20broke%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202019%2C%20after%20India%20repealed%20Article%20370%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20and%20announced%20Aksai%20Chin%20as%20a%20Union%20Territory%2C%20China%20registered%20their%20protest%20against%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAksai%20Chin%20is%20territory%20in%20Ladakh%2C%20which%20both%20India%20and%20China%20stake%20their%20claims.%20Post%20that%2C%20that%20multiple%20clashes%20occurred%20along%20the%20LAC.%20The%20clashes%20that%20have%20been%20reported%20include%20the%20one%20at%20Pangong%20Tso%20on%20May%205%2C%20Sikkim%20on%20May%209%20and%20at%20Galwan%20Valley%20on%20June%2015%2C%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20negotiations%20have%20been%20ongoing%20between%20India%20and%20China.%20While%20China%20has%20publicly%20staked%20their%20claim%20on%20parts%20of%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20renaming%20some%20towns%2C%20details%20about%20physical%20confrontation%20with%20Indian%20soldiers%20were%20never%20made%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20details%20about%20the%20violent%20clashes%20along%20the%20LAC%20depict%20strategic%20acumen%2C%20and%20courage%20of%20Indian%20Army%20personnel%20operating%20in%20challenging%20and%20often%20undisclosed%20circumstances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20removal%20of%20the%20gallantry%20awards%20video%20from%20YouTube%20highlights%20the%20high%20level%20of%20secrecy%20involved%20in%20the%20cross-border%20matters%20and%20also%20raises%20questions%20about%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20unwillingness%20to%20reveal%20the%20details%20about%20the%20actual%20situation%20between%20India%20and%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3