rl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Case%20in%20Apex%20Court%2C%20Union%20Govt%20Forms%20Panel%20For%20Equitable%20Distribution%20of%20Benefits%20Among%20SC%20Groups%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F18150906%2FSupreme-Court.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Union%20government%20has%20constituted%20a%20committee%20of%20secretaries%20under%20the%20cabinet%20secretary%20to%20work%20out%20equitable%20distribution%20of%20government%20benefits%20among%20the%20backward%20communities%20of%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Famid-calls-for-sub-categorisation-of-scs-government-forms-panel-to-look-into-even-distribution-of-benefits%2Farticle67752808.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20will%20have%20five%20members%20and%20will%20focus%20on%20the%20distribution%20of%20schemes%20and%20initiatives%20among%20hitherto%20ignored%20groups%20and%20not%20into%20questions%20of%20reservation%20or%20the%20division%20of%20employment%20and%20education%20quotas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20because%20a%20a%20seven-judge%20constitution%20bench%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20will%20soon%20consider%20whether%20sub-categorisation%20of%20Scheduled%20Caste%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20communities%20is%20permissible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20will%20look%20at%20the%20sub-classification%20exercise%20vis-a-vis%20the%20economically%20backward%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20sources%20added%20that%20nothing%20prevented%20it%20from%20forming%20an%20opinion%20on%20the%20matter%20in%20the%20process%2C%20for%20the%20consideration%20of%20the%20government%20whenever%20appropriate%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20has%20the%20secretaries%20of%20the%20Union%20ministries%20of%20Home%2C%20Law%2C%20Tribal%20Affairs%2C%20and%20Social%20Justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20no%20deadline%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERight%20before%20the%20assembly%20election%20in%20Telangana%20last%20year%2C%20reports%20had%20claimed%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20set%20the%20ball%20rolling%20to%20establish%20a%C2%A0%20committee%20to%20look%20into%20the%20sub-categorisation%20of%20the%20Madiga%20community.%20The%20Madigas%20are%20part%20of%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705651232000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F18150906%2FSupreme-Court.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fcase-in-apex-court-union-govt-forms-panel-for-equitable-distribution-of-benefits-among-sc-groups%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20seven-judge%20constitution%20bench%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20will%20parallely%20consider%20whether%20sub-categorisation%20of%20Scheduled%20Caste%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20communities%20is%20permissible.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fcase-in-apex-court-union-govt-forms-panel-for-equitable-distribution-of-benefits-among-sc-groups%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Home%20Office%20'hires%20aircraft%20hangar'%20to%20practise%20forcing%20asylum%20seekers%20on%20to%20Rwanda%20flights%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705650360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F22%2F09%2F768x432%2Fskynews-plane-boris-johnson_5884141.jpg%3F20220902020708%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fhome-office-hires-aircraft-hangar-to-practise-forcing-asylum-seekers-on-to-rwanda-flights-13051396%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20aircraft%20hangar%20and%20fuselage%20have%20been%20hired%20by%20the%20Home%20Office%20for%20security%20officials%20to%20practise%20forcing%20asylum%