ur%3B%20Clocks%20Rs%202.5%20Crore%20In%20Revenue%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20common%20topic%20of%20discussion%20in%20my%20house%20whenever%20one%20of%20us%20falls%20sick%20revolves%20around%20our%20unhealthy%20diets.%20The%20conversation%20tends%20to%20escalate%20with%20my%20mother%20passionately%20emphasising%20how%20diets%20in%20the%20past%20were%20enriched%20with%20superfoods%20like%20%3Cem%3Ejowar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Ebajra%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrue%20enough%2C%20millets%20are%20now%20being%20recognised%20as%20superfoods%20worldwide.%20In%202023%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F137728%2Findian-government-ban-e-cigarettes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20government%20%3C%2Fa%3Edesignated%20it%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9CYear%20of%20Millets%E2%80%9D%20to%20underscore%20their%20numerous%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20challenge%20arises%20due%20to%20the%20limited%20availability%20of%20dedicated%20stores%20offering%20a%20variety%20of%20millets.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20our%20fast-paced%20world%2C%20what%20most%20of%20us%20need%20is%20ready-to-use%20recipes%2C%20and%20not%20many%20producers%20offer%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20millet%20options.%20Recognising%20this%20gap%2C%20I%20founded%20my%20own%20millet%20startup%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sai%20Krishna%20Popuri%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Health%20Sutra%2C%20as%20shared%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESai%2C%20the%20entrepreneur%20behind%20a%20millet-based%20brand%2C%20offers%20a%20diverse%20range%20of%20millet%20products%20through%20his%20startup.%20From%20Jowar%20Flakes%20to%20Millet%20Muesli%20and%20Millet%20Idli%20Rawa%20pre-mix%2C%20the%20brand%20aims%20to%20seamlessly%20integrate%20this%20superfood%20into%20your%20daily%20diet.%20With%20thousands%20of%20products%20sold%2C%20the%20brand%20has%20achieved%20an%20impressive%