%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-338561%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESai%20quit%20his%20job%20to%20start%20a%20millet-based%20startup%20called%20Health%20Sutra.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Health%20Sutra%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFood%20startups%20have%20always%20been%20an%20area%20of%20interest%20for%20Sai.%20%E2%80%9CFood%20tech%20has%20always%20been%20interesting%20to%20me.%20Before%20Health%20Sutra%2C%20I%20was%20working%20on%20an%20Indo-Chinese%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F289275%2Fhyderabad-startup-banyan-nation-recycles-plastic-waste-into-fmcg-product-bottles%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estartup%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAround%20the%20same%20time%2C%20my%20father%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20diabetes.%20The%20doctor%20recommended%20various%20alternatives%20such%20as%20wheat%2C%20oats%2C%20or%20quinoa%20for%20his%20diet.%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20help%20but%20wonder%20%E2%80%93%20oats%20are%20fine%2C%20but%20quinoa%20is%20imported%20from%20South%20America.%20Why%20opt%20for%20something%20from%20halfway%20across%20the%20world%20when%20we%20have%20equally%20good%20options%20right%20here%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWanting%20to%20find%20alternatives%20in%20India%2C%20he%20went%20looking%20for%20options.%20He%20met%20a%20relative%20who%20worked%20in%20the%20food%20science%20department%20at%20a%20university%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20was%20passionately%20discussing%20millets%20and%20how%20they%20are%20poised%20to%20become%20the%20next%20big%20thing.%20Millets%2C%20being%20deeply%20rooted%20in%20our%20land%2C%20boast%20indigenous%20qualities%2C%20robustness%2C%20and%20drought%20resistance%2C%20making%20them%20a%20highly%20beneficial%20choice%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20further%20research%2C%20Sai%20realised%20the%20reason%20why%20the%20superfood%20was%20not%20as%20popular%20as%20others.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20processing%20technology%20for%20wheat%2C%20rice%2C%20and%20corn%20has%20advanced%20significantly.%20However%2C%20the%20same%20cannot%20be%20said%20for%20millets.%20The%20limited%20progress%20in%20milling%20and%20further%20processing%20of%20millets%20creates%20a%20situation%20where%20presenting%20millets%20to%20consumers%20in%20a%20modern%20context%2C%20or%20offering%20them%20a%20contemporary%20perspective%20on%20their%20traditional%20foods%20and%20roots%2C%20becomes%20challenging%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20change%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F336185%2Fraimati-ghiuria-preserves-traditional-millets-at-her-odisha-farm%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eperspective%20towards%20millet%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20to%20make%20it%20more%20easily%20accessible%20to%20consumers%2C%20Sai%20started%20his%20research%20and%20development%20in%202013.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20grandmas%20were%20right%20to%20ask%20us%20to%20include%20millets%20in%20our%20diets%20as%20they%20are%20traditionally%20considered%20to%20be%20healthy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%202014%2C%20he%20was%20ready%20with%20his%20first%20product.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20launched%20jowar%20porridge%20under%20our%20brand%20Health%20Sutra%20and%20it%20got%20a%20great%20response%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20its%20launch%2C%20the%20company%20has%20experienced%20significant%20growth%2C%20introducing%20a%20diverse%20range%20of%20products.%20These%20include%20cereal%20flakes%20such%20as%20Jowar%20Flakes%2C%20Ragi%20Flakes%2C%20and%20Barley%20Flakes%2C%20as%20well%20as%20seven%20different%20types%20of%20rava%20for%20idli%20and%20%3Cem%3Eupma%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20biscuits%20made%20from%20ragi%20and%20jo