enting%2C%20but%20it%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20become%20a%20daily%20habit%20like%20eating%20rice%20or%20chapati.%20That%2C%20I%20believe%2C%20will%20take%20some%20more%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20products%20by%20Health%20Sutra%20are%20currently%20available%20in%20close%20to%203%2C000%20supermarkets%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Telangana.%20They%20also%20ship%20them%20country-wide%20via%20Amazon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-8-1705584692.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sai%20is%20planning%20on%20entering%20the%20kids'%20market%20by%20making%20millet%20more%20digestible%2C%20palatable%2C%20and%20accessible.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-8-1705584692.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-8-1705584692-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-8-1705584692-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-8-1705584692-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-8-1705584692-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-338560%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESai%20is%20planning%20on%20entering%20the%20kids%E2%80%99%20market%20by%20making%20millet%20more%20digestible%2C%20palatable%2C%20and%20accessible.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Health%20Sutra%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20been%20a%20while%20since%20P%20Lalitha%20found%20the%20benefits%20of%20millet%20but%20was%20looking%20for%20ideas%20to%20incorporate%20it%20into%20her%20kid%E2%80%99s%20diet.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20using%20Health%20Sutra%E2