CThe%20greatest%20factor%20to%20consider%20was%20that%20the%20temperature%20needed%20to%20grow%20saffron%20was%20only%20in%20Kashmir%20in%20India.%20So%20I%20had%20to%20mimic%20that%20here%20in%20Solan.%20I%20used%20the%20lab%20whose%20temperature%20can%20be%20controlled%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20mimicking%20the%20environment%20and%20planting%20the%20seeds%2C%20it%20was%20important%20for%20me%20to%20keep%20a%20close%20eye%20on%20the%20buds.%20I%20was%20not%20aware%20that%20they%20can%20catch%20fungus%20and%20was%20taken%20aback%20when%20my%20first%20crop%20did%20catch%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20able%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20it%20by%20drying%20the%20affected%20plants%20and%20separating%20them%20from%20the%20healthy%20ones%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20nearly%208%20months%20of%20hard%20labour%20and%20planning%2C%20Gaurav%20was%20able%20to%20grow%20500%20grams%20of%20saffron%20in%20his%20aeroponics%20farm.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20produce%2C%20although%20not%20a%20lot%2C%20was%20a%20good%20sign.%20I%20was%20very%20tense%20because%20this%20was%20a%20leap%20of%20faith%20for%20me.%20Earlier%2C%20I%20had%20no%20intentions%20of%20doing%20anything%20and%20seeing%20those%20buds%20flower%20was%20a%20great%20feeling%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-6-1705413451.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gaurav%20sold%20his%20first%20produce%20at%20a%20price%20of%20Rs%20500%20per%20gram.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-6-1705413451.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-6-1705413451-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen